OL,6,FThe defendant was also described as
OL,7,Fhaving had a sexual interest involving
OL,8,Ffeet - a 'foot fetish' that police say
OL,9,Fgoes back many years.
OL,11,FIn the dock during the trial, Glas
OL,12,Fwould often have his eyes closed -
OL,13,Fsometimes looking up to the ceiling
OL,14,Fand rocking back and forth, holding
OL,15,Fprayer beads in his right hand.
OL,17,FHe will be sentenced on Friday 11
OL,18,FApril and will be remanded in custody
OL,19,Funtil that date.
